   Hey Kids! Welcome to the Town site designed especially for you. Within
   the next few months you will begin to see some fun and exciting new
   changes to our kids section, so check back with us. For now click on
   these cool links below.

   Check the Youth Programs and Youth Athletic Programs under the Parks &
   Recreation section.

   Brush up on your Babysitting Safety Tips and learn about Bicycle
   Safety, Laws and Registration, with help from the Blacksburg Police
   Department.

   Print out the Fire Safety Coloring Pages 1 and 2 from the Volunteer
   Fire Department web site.

   Skip to the Blacksburg Transit's Kids' Stop, on the BT site.

   Visit the Kid's Page of the National Weather Service, Blacksburg, Va.

   Check out the web sites for Montgomery County Schools in Blacksburg:
     * Blacksburg Middle
     * Blacksburg High
     * Gilbert Linkous Elementary
     * Harding Avenue Elementary
     * Kipps Elementary
     * Margaret Beeks Elementary
     * Price's Fork Elementary

